net.shibboleth.ext.spring.resource

Class SVNBasicAuthenticationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tmatesoft.svn.core.auth.BasicAuthenticationManager
      • net.shibboleth.ext.spring.resource.SVNBasicAuthenticationManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean, org.tmatesoft.svn.core.auth.ISVNAuthenticationManager, org.tmatesoft.svn.core.auth.ISVNProxyManager, org.tmatesoft.svn.core.auth.ISVNProxyManagerEx, org.tmatesoft.svn.core.auth.ISVNSSHHostVerifier

    @ThreadSafe
public class SVNBasicAuthenticationManager
extends org.tmatesoft.svn.core.auth.BasicAuthenticationManager
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean
    Authentication manager for SVN resources based on BasicAuthenticationManager.
    Exbeds the proxy information into individual beans to allow setting from Spring.
